{
  "stem": "323.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had a woman at home taking care of the kids, which meant that I really didn't earn any money.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The money that I made went to pay for child care and things like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I loved it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I loved every moment of my job-- of the work with Doyle Dane Bernbach, while it was still the firm that it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And most of-- we were friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did things outside the office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was just like an extended family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was-- then after I started working full time, I became more and more involved in my job.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My children always came first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, I don't want to say that I didn't do that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I did become more involved in my job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My marriage turned bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Things began to happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think I put more emphasis on work than on anything else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now the happiest day in my whole life that I ever had was the day my daughter was born.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this is an experience I don't think you can-- I mean, I think probably most mothers had the same experience.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it's really, it's something horrendous, to have this baby that part's of you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I tried to teach my children [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] above all, to be true to themselves, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and not to become part of a pack, to be individuals.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I gave them the love for the out of doors, because that was very important to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they now go camping with their children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So somehow it's carried on, from one generation to the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You still ski?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I ski, I skate, I swim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I swim three times a week.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
